  "system": {
    "description": {
      "value": "\n<p><b>Type:</b> Ninjutsu (Raiton)</p>\n<p><b>Rank:</b> 8</p>\n<p><b>Chakra Cost:</b> 8</p>\n\n<p><b>Learn DC:</b> 24 | <b>Successes:</b> 4</p>\n<p><b>Perform:</b> 11 | <b>Perform DC:</b> 25</p>\n\n<p><b>Components:</b> H</p>\n\n<hr>\n\n<p>Upon completion of this technique, the user condenses his Raikiri into a long blade of lightning. Thus formed, the Raikiri no Kendo has the same characteristics as a katana, in which the user is automatically proficient, that deals an additional 1d6 points of electricity damage and 1d4 points of sonic damage on a successful attack. Raikiri no Kendo attacks are chakra-enhanced.<br><br>If the user scores a critical hit with the Raikiri no Kendo, the user doubles the slashing damage only, and the target must succeed a Fortitude save (as per the technique) or become stunned for 1 round afterwards. Once sundered, or if it leaves the user's hand or the duration expires, the Raikiri no Kendo fades into nothingness.<br><br>If the user has an active Raikiri in his hand, he may use this technique as a swift action that does not provoke an attack of opportunity. His Raikiri transforms into the Raikiri no Kendo if the technique is performed this way.</p>\n\n<hr><p><b>Requires:</b> Raikiri (3)</p>\n<p><b>Effect:</b> One Raikiri no Kendo</p>\n",
      "summary": "",
      "instructions": ""
    },
